data.description:
Do not miss out on this spacious Anamosa home located right on the edge of Anamosa as you head out toward beautiful Grant Wood country!


Boasting 3 Bedrooms (with plenty of room for more downstairs if needed), 2.5 Bathrooms, and a 2 Stall PULL-THROUGH garage; make this your home for next holiday season! Whether you need space for a growing family or room for the family to visit, this place will work for you!

In the FULLY FENCED back yard you will find your very own custom pond stocked with goldfish, a small shed for wood or yard equipment. Windows throughout the home have all been replaced in the last 1-4 years.

Additional features of the home include a spacious Storm Cellar & a Private Well (not currently running).
